metadata.name: Effluence #317
metadata.description:
“Through our eyes, the universe is perceiving itself. Through our ears, the universe is listening to its harmonies. We are the witnesses through which the universe becomes conscious of its glory, of its magnificence.”

-Alan Wilson Watts


---

Depending on the feature values, this artwork may take several seconds to render.
A modern, capable computer is advised.

To download image at different resolutions, press keys:

1. Low
2. Mid
3. High

---

10 first people minting at auction start price can request high-quality print at no additional cost (DM on Twitter for more details if interested)

Made with p5.js, curiosity and goodwill.

---

Daniel Aguilar
October 2022

Twitter: @protozoo
Instagram: @prtzart
Website: https://protozoo.xyz

metadata.name: BRUTALIST MANIFESTO #35
metadata.description:
Discovered and brought into daylight from under gigantic concrete pylons of ancient digital monuments by brutologists. 

Written on multiple screens with blocks and bytes and bits in a language long forgotten.

Decyphering has already started for the sole purpose of understanding the roots of the new Brutalist Movement. 

These are the fragments of the BRUTALIST MANIFESTO.

///

Tech specs already decrypted from the fragments:

Randomized parameters
- 12 color palettes
- 5-8-10 rows
- 5-8-10 columns
- 0-8 blocks per glyphs
- 0-all special glyphs per row
- very rare occasion of a glitched glyph

Press 's' to download an image in 2k at any time of the generation.

///

Have fun decyphering!

☁︎

cloudnoise © 2022

///

Created with P5.js library.
